"INCREASE ATTRIBUTE"

Category: ^gHEALTH^n
Duration: ^gSUSTAINED^n

This spell affects its particularly aligned attribute, this varient 
only affects non-cyberware modified attributes. The TN is the targetted
stat which is increased by 1 for every two successes, with a maximum 
increase up to the force it is cast at.

^WSee Also: CAST, DECREASE ATTRIBUTE, INCREASE CYBERED ATTRIBUTE, DECREASE CYBERED ATTRIBUTE^n
